Hayden Stevenson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hayden_Stevenson 0 Hayden Stevenson (July 2, 1877 – January 31, 1952) was an American film actor. He appeared in 108 films between 1915 and 1942. He was born in Georgetown, Kentucky and died in Los Angeles, California. Hayden_Stevenson ( July_2_,_1877 – January_31_,_1952 ) was an_American_film_actor .
